Day 19: Conflict is a Catalyst!
🔥 "Conflict isn’t a roadblock—it’s a path to growth!"  
👉 Tip: Don’t shy away from conflict. Use it to drive discussions and spark innovation when resolved constructively.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
